snippet.title: Aqua Park Tycoon
snippet.description:
Build gift shops, animal enclosures and more to bring in visitors and keep them happy. Quickly expand your park as you train cute seals, penguins, otters and dolphins to perform fun tricks for your visitors. Adjust the prices for entry fees, snacks and souvenirs to maximize profits and attendance. At the Aqua Park, you're in charge! Includes 26 types of buildings, 4 animals to adopt, 3D views, mini-games, in-game tutorial and 10 player avatars.

http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/aqua-park-tycoon/id408489182
http://www.selectsoft.com/
